item.description:
arXiv:2505.07822v1 Announce Type: new 
Abstract: In this paper, we study the Hyers-Ulam stability of the following equation \begin{multline*}
  \phi(x+y-z)+\phi(x+z-y)+\phi(y+z-x)=\phi (x-y)+\phi(x-z)+\phi(z-y)
  +\phi(x)+\phi(y) +\phi(z) \end{multline*}
  in modular space, with or without $\Delta_2$-condition, and in $\beta$-homogeneous Banach space.
